/devops/linux-patching-lab
│
├── ansible-controller (VM)  → control plane
│
├── ubuntu-node              → Linux target (Debian family)
├── suse-node                → Linux target (SUSE family)
│
├── inventory/               → host definitions
├── group_vars/              → configuration management
├── playbooks/               → automation logic
├── node_monitoring/        → metrics + reporting module
│
└── GitHub Actions (external) → CI/CD trigger layer

Goal:

Create CI/CD pipelines to run pre-check, patching and post-patching, activities automated

